data.description: Charming & beautifully remodelled historic farmhouse on nearly 50 acres of prime pasture land! Kitchen was completely remodelled in 2023- new floors, cabinets, counters, back splash, paint, fixtures, etc. SS fridge 2 yr old, SS dishwasher 5 yr old. 2023 primary bath remodel- NEW vanity, linen closet, tub/shower, toilet, doors, paint, etc. ENTIRE second floor remodelled 2020 w/ new sheetrock, electrical, fixtures, & flooring. NEW H2O heater. Trane heat pump. NEW 2022 detached garage w/ RV carport. Renovated 1/2 bath in 2023 w/ NEW vanity, commode & flooring. NEW exterior vinyl, gutters, soffit. Second home site w/ well & septic at top of pasture (past barn). Multiple sheds, outbuildings & barns. FIBER internet available! Looking for a beautiful country retreat w/ plenty of grazing land for your cattle/horses/sheep/etc, look no further! Turnkey and ready for new owners!
